description:
In episode 796, Jack and Miles are joined by Alison Rosen Is Your New Best Friend's Alison Rosen to discuss Joe Biden having to reverse a lot of Trump's bullshit, a quick look at the history of Republican presidents, Trump regret, the future of Trump, Youtuber Blippi's viral poop past, and more!

FOOTNOTES:

  1. Biden signs executive actions on COVID, climate change, immigration and more
  2. Ted Cruz clashes with Seth Rogen over Biden rejoining Paris climate deal
  3. Parler turns on Trump
  4. Ok, where did we go wrong?
  5. Kids YouTube Star Blippi “Regrets” The Viral Video In Which He Poops All Over His Friend
  6. WATCH: Madison McFerrin: Learn Your Lesson
